725661f-a.title: Queens: 81st Street - 34th Avenue
725661f-a.text:
81st Street (left), east side, north from 34th Avenue to
Northern Boulevard, showing a group of apartment buildings
called ''The Towers.'' These buildings are also on the west side
of 82nd Street and extend as far north as Northern Boulevard.
The 34th Avenue side of the two corner buildings are also shown.
The avenue has a tree-lined isle.
Ewing Calloway  About 1928
NO REPRODUCTIONS

725662f-a.title: Queens: 81st Street - 34th Avenue
725662f-a.text:
81st Street, at the N.E. corner of 34th Avenue, showing a
corner of ''The Towers,'' a large group of apartment houses.
The view is eastward across tennis courts lying between 79th and
80th Streets.
Brown Brothers  About 1928
NO REPRODUCTIONS
